Class EnArc

java.lang.Object
org.pneditor.petrinet.models.lachguer.souissi.Arc
org.pneditor.petrinet.models.lachguer.souissi.EnArc
public class EnArc extends Arc
EnArc (Entering Arc) class extending Arc. Represents an arc that adds tokens to a place during a transition.
